name: Koolwheeler 12V Cooler
shortdescription: shortdescription
longdescription: Includes:. 1 Sliding shelf. 12-Volt power cord. Instruction Manual. Cools to 40 to 45°F below the outside temperature. State-of-the-art thermoelectric cooling technology. Reverse the power cord to turn the cooler into a warmer. Fits 57 (12 Oz.) soda cans. Can sit in chest position or upright like a refrigerator. Shelf included can be used in multiple positions as trays or dividers. Large capacity is ideal for long trips, family get together or for tailgate parties. Power: 4 amps, 48W. Capacity: 57-355 ml (12 Oz.) cans, 34 L (36 Qts.). 1-Year manufacturer's warranty. 16.7 in. L x 22.1 in. W x 16.5 in. H (16 lbs.). The W75 Kool Wheeler Cooler uses a 12 Volt thermoelectric module powered by the cigarette lighter in your vehicle to cool your favorite drinks and snacks to 45 to 50 Fahrenheit degrees below the ambient temperature. 12 Volt coolers and warmers will heat or cool your lunch and beverages. You can use 12 Volt Coolers in your car, RV, boat, truck, dorm or just at home as spare fridge. So while you relax and enjoy quiet, dependable 12 volt cooling, other campers and drivers are stuck in the "Ice Age", standing in line to buy overpriced ice or driving from store to store looking for an ice. By reversing the power cord you can also turn the W-75 Kool Wheeler into a warmer to keep "fast food" or "take out food" hot on the way home. Take a full load of hot chocolate or coffee to the gang in winter, or a hot casserole and other hot food to family gatherings. The W-75 Kool Wheeler is so versatile you'll never want to leave home without it!

shortdescription: shortdescription
longdescription: <ul><li>Dimensions: 20L x 18.75W x 36H in.</li><li>White microwave and refrigerator combo</li><li>2.5-cubic-foot refrigerator; 0.7-cubic-foot microwave</li><li>Reversible, locking refrigerator door</li><li>Automatic defrost feature</li><li>Power allocator limits overall use to 10 amps</li></ul><p>While it's not quite a skyscraper, the <strong>Summit MRF28L Auto Defrost All-Refrigerator</strong> has got the same idea in response to a space-crunch. The reversible, locking door on the spacious mini-fridge keeps food safe and sound, despite any covetous colleagues. The clean white finish is versatile and modern, and the included power allocator keeps energy use to 10 amps. Think of this handy set as the skyscraper of home appliances.</p><p><strong>About Summit Appliance</strong> Summit Appliance was founded in 1969 and has been a leading supplier of compact, specialty, commercial and medical refrigerators, and freezers ever since. Carrying well over 600 models of specialty refrigerators and freezers, Summit also delivers the largest range of fully automatic defrost compacts available on the market. With their expanding line of built-in and freestanding units, Summit serves a variety of household, commercial, and scientific markets. Even after extensive international expansion, Summit Appliance continues to remain a private, family-owned business with no outside investors. From innovative design to superior construction, SUMMIT products embody quality from the inside out.</p>
